snippet.title: Cabbage Patch Kids Adventures in the Park (ColecoVision)
snippet.description: When I was younger, I've been told that there were 500 Scenes in this game and Scene 500 was supposed to involve almost if not every feature in the game and be VERY tough. Well, that was a lie... 30 years later, I finally get an answer... ;)
